Texas Air Corp's Continental Airlinessaid it will begin service in April to Bakersfield, Calif., andEugene and Medford, Ore., from its hub at Denver.    From Denver, Continental will fly a daily nonstop and aone-stop flight to each of the three cities, the company said.Service to the Oregon cities will start April 5 and toBakersfield, April 22. Reuter&#3;